{"tid":2304129,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"你安心，我好唔安心 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-11-28T13:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T13:32:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0aad5492e83dd7d77ac68272012fa9f610085f","tid":2304129,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:29:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201128/2Q7IEQHFDZCZPGQDFR27LFI3SU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201128%2F2Q7IEQHFDZCZPGQDFR27LFI3SU%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR%2BUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=d7a1c23c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201128%2F2Q7IEQHFDZCZPGQDFR27LFI3SU%2F&h=63fd622f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201128/2Q7IEQHFDZCZPGQDFR27LFI3SU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n你安心，我好唔安心 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nKL8CRo9I5Lc4PM0JJ95RjlQB0w=/1142x715/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CBYQVMJM6FB7BN7D22TZJPQP7E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnKL8CRo9I5Lc4PM0JJ95RjlQB0w%3D%2F1142x715%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCBYQVMJM6FB7BN7D22TZJPQP7E.png&h=8b63df24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果日報》截圖<br />\n<br />\n香港朋友傳來一則公司通告，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n也就是說，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港共政府在香港強推「安心出行」App，其實就是香港版的中國社會信用評級機制。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎爆發至今，香港人一直不相信港共政府，自主抗疫，成績還算不俗。但港府由始至終不對中國封關，甚至允諾長居中國的港人回港免隔離，防疫還是迎疫，動機令人質疑。<br />\n<br />\n疫情擴散下，先推「自願檢測」計劃，失敗後，索性撕破面皮推欲強制檢測。更逼迫港人安裝「安心出行」App，整件事，就是一個陰謀，就是要把香港變成700萬人的大監倉。<br />\n<br />\n有說《國安法》雖惡，敵不過「安心出行」，因為前者不能把每一個人送進監獄，即使被控，也要上庭。但後者直接把700萬人變成囚徒。不要以為疫情消失後，健康碼會廢除，它會永遠跟隨着你，監察你的一言一行，確保你政治正確，否則，隨時限制你行動自由，包括出入境自由。到時，不需要法庭手令，也不必沒收你的護照，一個健康碼，就可以將你攔截在機場，你哪兒也去不了。"},{"pid":"96385c798aaa497106e4b689b779cde074ce6d86","tid":2304129,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}